description:
EliteShipper is a blockchain-based project that intends to fundamentally change the container shipping industry through the development of industry-driven token called EliteShipperToken (ESHIP) supported by an EliteShipper Ecosystem.

EliteShipperToken (ESHIP) is an ERC20 compliant digital token distributed through the Ethereum network and will be tradeable in various cryptocurrency exchanges globally.
name: EliteShipperToken
